 <arm>
   <uof name="Topologically_Bounded_Surface">
     <description>
The Topologically_Bounded_Surface UoF specifies the definitional information for the concept of a face with fully defined geometry and explicit topology defining the boundaries. The permissible types of face geometry include elementary surfaces and B-spline surfaces. Edges are required to have their geometry defined by curves, that may include pcurves.
     </description>
